OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1779719229
OL,3,CStarmer urges TNT Sports to show
OL,4,CChampions League final for free
OL,6,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer has urged
OL,7,FTNT Sports to show the Champions
OL,8,FLeague final for free rather than
OL,9,Fputting it behind a paywall.
OL,11,FNext Saturday's match between Arsenal
OL,12,Fand Paris Saint-Germain will air on
OL,13,FTNT Sports at 5pm, behind a #4.99
OL,14,Fpaywall, and Starmer has said "hard-
OL,15,Fworking people should not have to
OL,16,Fworry about forking out for a
OL,17,Fsubscription to watch a game of this
OL,18,Fmagnitude".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1779719229
OL,3,CStarmer urges TNT Sports to show
OL,4,CChampions League final for free
OL,6,FThe #4.99 fee is for an HBO Max
OL,7,Fsubscription, which gives you access
OL,8,Fto TNT Sports coverage of the final
OL,9,Fand other Uefa cup finals.
OL,11,FAs a keen Arsenal fan, Starmer
OL,12,Faddressed his concerns in an open
OL,13,Fletter on Saturday.
OL,15,F"I was saddened to see that, for the
OL,16,Ffirst time since the competition
OL,17,Fstarted 34 years ago, TNT Sports has
OL,18,Fdecided that the Champions League
OL,19,Ffinal will not be free to watch for
OL,20,Ffootball supporters here in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1779719229
OL,3,CStarmer urges TNT Sports to show
OL,4,CChampions League final for free
OL,6,F"The Champions League is the biggest
OL,7,Fclub football competition in the world
OL,8,Fand rightly means a lot to fans in
OL,9,Fthis country ` the home of football. I
OL,10,Fam a firm believer that the final of
OL,11,Fthis competition should remain free to
OL,12,Fwatch, whether Arsenal have made it or
OL,13,Fnot.
OL,15,F"Obviously, I want as many fellow fans
OL,16,Fas possible to be able to watch our
OL,17,Fteam in this historic final for the
OL,18,Ffirst time in 20 years. However, this
OL,19,Fis bigger than that.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1779719229
OL,3,CStarmer urges TNT Sports to show
OL,4,CChampions League final for free
OL,6,F"This is about supporters of all teams
OL,7,Fcoming together in living rooms and
OL,8,Fpubs in every corner of the country to
OL,9,Fwatch the most elite players in Europe
OL,10,Fbattle it out."
OL,12,FSome Arsenal fans were left in tears
OL,13,Fafter the team were crowned Premier
OL,14,FLeague champions
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
