OL,3,CStarmer urges TNT Sports to show
OL,4,CChampions League final for free
OL,6,FThe final is especially significant
OL,7,Ffor millions of British Arsenal fans
OL,8,Fafter the club won the Premier League
OL,9,Ffor the first time in 22 years, giving
OL,10,Fthem the chance to complete a historic
OL,11,Fdouble by winning their first-ever
OL,12,FChampions League title.
OL,14,FIt is only the second time Arsenal
OL,15,Fhave reached the final, the first
OL,16,Fsince 2006, with reigning champions
OL,17,FPSG standing between Mikel Arteta's
OL,18,Fside and one of the greatest nights in
OL,19,Fthe club's history.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1779719229
OL,3,CStarmer urges TNT Sports to show
OL,4,CChampions League final for free
OL,6,FStarmer added: "We should be putting
OL,7,Fsupporters first. That is why I have
OL,8,Falready encouraged FIFA to do more to
OL,9,Fmake tickets more affordable at this
OL,10,Fsummer's World Cup.
OL,12,F"That is also why I want to strongly
OL,13,Furge you to reconsider and make the
OL,14,Ffinal next Saturday free to watch for
OL,15,Fthe millions of passionate football
OL,16,Ffans in this country."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
