OL,3,CStarmer urges TNT Sports to show
OL,4,CChampions League final for free
OL,6,FSince the European Cup was rebranded
OL,7,Fas the Champions League 34 years ago,
OL,8,Fthe final has always been free to
OL,9,Fwatch, shown on ITV from 1992 to 2015,
OL,10,Fthen streamed for free by BT Sport and
OL,11,Fits successor TNT Sports for the past
OL,12,Fdecade.
OL,14,FBut this year, UK rights holder TNT
OL,15,FSports, owned by Warner Bros
OL,16,FDiscovery, confirmed to viewers that
OL,17,Fthey will only be able to watch the
OL,18,Ffinal on its own platform or HBO Max,
OL,19,Fboth of which require a subscription.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1779719229
OL,3,CStarmer urges TNT Sports to show
OL,4,CChampions League final for free
OL,6,FThe same applies to Crystal Palace's
OL,7,FConference League final against Rayo
OL,8,FVallecano on May 27, and was also the
OL,9,Fcase for Aston Villa's Europa League
OL,10,Ffinal win over SC Freiburg on
OL,11,FWednesday.
OL,13,FTNT Sports can be accessed through HBO
OL,14,FMax, BT, Sky, Virgin Media or Amazon,
OL,15,Fwith subscriptions typically costing
OL,16,Fbetween #25 and #34 a month, while a
OL,17,Fseparate HBO Max plan starts from
OL,18,F#4.99.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
