OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1779719229
OL,3,CStarmer urges TNT Sports to show
OL,4,CChampions League final for free
OL,6,F"We have made all three Uefa finals
OL,7,Fthis year available from just #4.99,
OL,8,Fthe price for a month-long
OL,9,Fsubscription to HBO Max that also
OL,10,Fincludes the great entertainment on
OL,11,Fthe service. This represents
OL,12,Fexceptional value for fans to watch
OL,13,Fthe conclusion of the competitions."
OL,15,FAccording to a report in The Guardian,
OL,16,FUefa was "irritated" by the sports
OL,17,Fbroadcaster's decision to put all
OL,18,Fthree European finals behind a
OL,19,Fpaywall, having previously made them
OL,20,Favailable to stream for free.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
