OL,3,CStarmer urges TNT Sports to show
OL,4,CChampions League final for free
OL,6,FTNT Sports is set to lose the TV
OL,7,Frights to all three European
OL,8,Fcompetitions from the 2027-28 season,
OL,9,Fhaving been outbid by Paramount for
OL,10,Fthe Champions League and by Sky Sports
OL,11,Ffor the Europa League and Conference
OL,12,FLeague in last year's Uefa media
OL,13,Frights auction.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
